    },
    {
      "_id": "bf25a1e9472107b7",
      "name": "Making an Initiative Check",
      "sort": 7,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-8068-81bf-d36d0398f7fd\">Roll a <strong>d20 </strong>and add your Combat Mastery and Agility to the result. Bonuses and Penalties to Agility Checks don't effect Initiative Checks, unless otherwise stated.</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80b7-bf54-fb0169f30f01\"><strong><span style=\"border-bottom:0.05em solid\">Initiative Check Formula</span></strong></p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-800e-a9c7-c1be16f1ad5c\">d20 + Combat Mastery + Agility</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-807c-90b1-c1ff99a042f6\" class=\"block-color-purple_background\"><strong>DC Tip:</strong> Initiative Checks are not considered Agility Checks for the purposes of DisADV due to Heavy Armor with the Rigid Property or other things that affect Agility Checks.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 3,
        "show": true
      },
      "type": "text",
      "system": {},
      "image": {},
