    {
      "_id": "c782aa456bfe79cd",
      "name": "Party Outcomes",
      "sort": 9,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80b6-be0a-f84dd325e8ee\">Use the following Success and Failure Statements to determine who will take the first turn in Combat.</p><ul id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80da-96b4-ca307b20e5c4\" class=\"bulleted-list\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><strong>Success:</strong> If at least 1/2 the PCs beat the Encounter DC, the PC Team wins the first Initiative Turn of the Combat.</li></ul><ul id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80ad-87f0-eab615333839\" class=\"bulleted-list\"><li style=\"list-style-type:disc\"><strong>Failure:</strong> If less than 1/2 the PCs beat the Encounter DC, the Enemy Team wins the first Initiative Turn of the Combat.</li></ul>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 3,
        "show": true
      },
