    {
      "_id": "15648e81bd7f0aa6",
      "name": "Initiative Order",
      "sort": 15,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-804b-bbc2-ebbc0baf960b\">The chosen Initiative Turns become the Initiative Order, which governs when each creature takes their respective Turns in each subsequent Round of Combat. Once the first Initiative Turn is assigned, Combat begins, all creatures gain access to their Action Points, the first Round of Combat begins.</p>",
