    {
      "_id": "b528f3385a43d9ea",
      "name": "Time in Combat",
      "sort": 17,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-8002-ba69-eb0a2b919b68\">A Round of Combat lasts 12 in-game seconds, so 5 Rounds equals 1 minute of in-game time. You can imagine each creature’s Turn happening near simultaneously to each other with some creatures acting split-seconds before others.</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-8052-8aa8-e214db8805bf\"><strong><span style=\"border-bottom:0.05em solid\">Time in Combat</span></strong></p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-8039-8357-cde4608ddbf5\" class=\"block-color-blue\">1 Round of Combat = 12 seconds</p><p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-807e-aa87-da3d18d57569\" class=\"block-color-blue\">5 Rounds of Combat = 1 minute</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 3,
        "show": true
      },
